About
                                TMNet







About
TM Net Sdn Bhd is a fully-owned subsidiary of Telekom Malaysia Berhad (TM). It is envisioned to support TM Group in the new business era where media is fast converging with access in addressing customers’ needs. As with the wave of triple or quadruple play that has been seen in more mature markets, its primary role is to create demand for media-related services. In 2007, the Malaysian Communications And Multimedia Commission granted TM Net the CASP license to operate IPTV services in Malaysia. TM Net’s main services is HyppTV, a local pay IPTV service that offers high-quality up-to-date content, and which forms a key component of TM’s triple  play offering via UniFi VIP packages.Having established its footprint as the TV of choice for flexibility in content and viewing options, HyppTV is fast evolving to offer even more premium channels, video-on-demandand interactive services.





Vision
To become Malaysian leading online company that inspires and encourages creative talents to produce strong, vibrant and indispensable online contents and applications.





Mission
To leverage on the creative talents and committed individuals in order to enrich customers’ experience in explore and sharing our services.














HyppTV

HyppTV is TM’s very own pay TV, delivered through UniFi. Enjoy world-class entertainment, award winning shows and channels in full HD from Live TV, Video On Demand and Interactive channel offering, rain or shine from as low as RM1/day!*
More info, please click this logo
 


























